text: Asheboro is a city in and the county seat of Randolph County, North Carolina, United States. The population was 27,156 at the 2020 census. It is the home of the state-owned North Carolina Zoo.NC Zoological Park Funding and Organization (PDF) Retrieved on 2010-10-08. ==References== Category:Cities in North Carolina Category:County seats in North Carolina
title: Asheboro, North Carolina
